VOID ID(main) LPAREN RPAREN
LBRACE
INT ID(i) COMMA ID(n) SEMICOLON
DOUBLE ID(s) SEMICOLON
ID(s) ASSIGN CT_REAL(0.000000) SEMICOLON
ID(put_s) LPAREN CT_STRING("n=") RPAREN SEMICOLON
ID(n) ASSIGN ID(get_i) LPAREN RPAREN SEMICOLON
FOR LPAREN ID(i) ASSIGN CT_INT(0) SEMICOLON ID(i) LT ID(n) SEMICOLON ID(i) ASSIGN ID(i) PLUS CT_INT(1) RPAREN LBRACE
ID(s) ASSIGN ID(s) PLUS ID(get_i) LPAREN RPAREN SEMICOLON
RBRACE
ID(put_s) LPAREN CT_STRING("mean=") RPAREN SEMICOLON
ID(put_d) LPAREN ID(s) DIV ID(n) RPAREN SEMICOLON
RBRACE
